{"tid":865513,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"打算整合一個資訊portal共享, 有冇得諗?","createTime":"2018-10-17T06:37:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T17:00:32.000Z","uid":214111,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e2f4d71ae9243746156ccd886f69676a684d5e09","tid":865513,"uid":214111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T06:37:40.000Z","msg":"未諗到用 google sheet 做定點<br />\n<br />\n不過個 idea 類似每個人都有唔同嘅熟悉範圍<br />\n例如我知睇 android 野去 xda, 睇去股票 aastock, dowwload 戲去 yify 等等...<br />\n<br />\n假如我而家想睇相機但我唔熟悉, 就要 Google search 關於相機嘅資料, 但有時 google 出黎會搵到d 類似 eprice 嘅打手文, 信左就大獲, 又或者個個網搵出黎嘅資料都幾零醉<br />\n又或者如果熟嘅人可能有一個大家比較公認嘅好網大部人都會睇佢 (例如 dcfever)<br />\n<br />\n當個資料庫愈黎愈大嘅時候, 日後大家搵野都方便同都行少好多冤枉路, 有冇得諗?"},{"pid":"da67df724ce3dbdb8d1253ac0bbe5bd0ebfb0f5b","tid":865513,"uid":95172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T06:55:07.000Z","msg":"唔想去某登，可以去邊？<br />\n答： <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efab6b15f51af2660848f7a660a7e1f5f09c565","tid":865513,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:21:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.quora.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.quora.com%2F&d=1Xpqqb4N39bP%2FPKbGsMeAp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=9f904404\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.quora.com/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstackoverflow.com%2F&d=1Xpqqb4N39bP%2FPKbGsMeAp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=e9ee8f34\" target=\"_blank\">https://stackoverflow.com/</a>"},{"pid":"da65b7705fbd72eb45ce354f938b30fd3ee849b2","tid":865513,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:34:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a47e3388a186278b760f201e06f56b68626de400","tid":865513,"uid":23699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:36:35.000Z","msg":"你點 make sure 你個網無打手"},{"pid":"716089588f52ada4977f0e99c7a45b99570e